      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "text": "这小妞儿既是此人所交托的，当然无话可说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "text": "哪！这小妞儿就在车内，孙当家的自己动手好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "江里白龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_gu_niang",
      "text": "方姑娘，我看你还是乖乖地跟着我走吧！逃有什么用呢？凭你身上这点儿本事，还想逃到哪里去吗？",
