      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fang_gu_niang",
      "text": "你快点跟人家去吧！不然……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "方姑娘",
      "listener": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "text": "走就走，你再拖姑娘可要骂你了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 361
