      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "武林中有些事辛兄是无法明了的，改日有机会再详谈吧。",
