      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "江里白龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_miao_shen_jun",
      "text": "神君久别江湖，想不到今日晚辈们却有幸得见神君一面，晚辈斗胆猜上一猜，神君深夜来到敝船，可是为了这个女子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_miao_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "七妙神君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "text": "阁下倒是聪明得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_li_bai_long",
      "speaker_name": "江里白龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_miao_shen_jun",
      "text": "既是神君的意思，晚辈哪敢违背，只是此女子乃别人交托给晚辈的……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
